message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>As a senior paralegal and legal assistant, I am equipped to assist in the real estate closing process by reviewing title searches to ensure there are no defects or encumbrances that could impact the transaction. However, I must clarify that my role does not extend to arbitrating disputes between parties. Arbitration would require a neutral third party, typically a professional arbitrator or legal counsel, to oversee and resolve the conflict. My responsibilities are centered around supporting the legal aspects of real estate transactions under the supervision of an attorney.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
